# Security Rules

Always:

- Validate external data using Zod
- Sanitize user input
- Use environment variables
- Validate uploads
- Use HTTPS
- save tokens in cookies 

Never:

- Expose secrets
- Trust frontend validation
- Store sensitive information in localStorage